{
  "stem": "18102.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that became the most dangerous thing my father had to decide to do or not do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I presume he did, although I didn't have any conversations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Remember now, I am eight years old at this time, and I wasn't getting all the details and secrets of his mind.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was getting a lot, because my parents kind of treated me as an adult.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was their only offspring, and they believed, as intellectuals often do, that children should know everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in effect, I was getting as much as they thought I ought to have, and it was quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard the word, 'the Dutch' mentioned, so that I knew there was an involvement with the Dutch embassy as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But no specifics that I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None that I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our visa was at the courtesy of the transit visa from Japan to [INAUDIBLE], yes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a child, I never knew of any other details than that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well in later years, when it became quite evident-- when we arrived in the United States and so many others did as a consequence of Sugihara-- we had many conversations that this was a great man.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That this man, in contravention of orders from the government of Japan, chose to follow his conscience rather than the dictates of government and issue visas to people who are desperate, and that this was their only way out.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Clearly, my father considered him a great man, 'a great humanitarian,' in his words, who had saved the lives of countless and countless people, and their families, and in effect their offspring, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He remembered his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He remembered that the name was Sugihara.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't remember his first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
